To cite Boids in publications, please use:

P. Calpin, Boids, (2016), GitHub repository, https://github.com/padraic-padraic/bad-boids

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is

@misc{Calpin2016,
  author = {Calpin, P.},
  title = {Boids},
  year = {2016},
  publisher = {GitHub},
  journal = {GitHub repository},
  howpublished = {\url{https://github.com/padraic-padraic/bad-boids},
}
